  "detailed_description": "Tiny Battles is a tactical action auto-battler where battles take place automatically in the arena.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BATTLES</h2>Battles happen automatically:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/6d11f8777ff0f0521fae80c4887cae8e.poster.avif?t=1706276140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/6d11f8777ff0f0521fae80c4887cae8e.webm?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/6d11f8777ff0f0521fae80c4887cae8e.mp4?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STRATEGY IS THE PATH TO VICTORY</h2>Build the right units for your strategy - early attack, midgame or consistent late game build with ultimate units for victory - the choice is yours.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/a545d651f6963e0fc52caa3c43cbe78a.poster.avif?t=1706276140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/a545d651f6963e0fc52caa3c43cbe78a.webm?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/a545d651f6963e0fc52caa3c43cbe78a.mp4?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBINE TROOPS </h2>Each faction has multiple paths to victory. Brute force, artillery attack or summoning creatures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/b8c2899e41adb80dc3446a29712f0f2b.poster.avif?t=1706276140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/b8c2899e41adb80dc3446a29712f0f2b.webm?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/b8c2899e41adb80dc3446a29712f0f2b.mp4?t=1706276140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STUDY YOUR OPPONENT</h2>Each enemy commander and his race have strengths and weaknesses, study them to defeat them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2759230/extras/2030fd34bdfc45f8d83dfdba97d82ee3.avif?t=1706276140\" width=600 height=226 /></span><br><br>",
